<TEXT>
German authorities yesterday announced the arrest of a 19-year-old youth on
suspicion of causing the arson attack which killed three Turks in the
northern town of Molln last week, writes Judy Dempsey in Bonn.
A woman and two girls died after a fire bomb was thrown into their home, an
